latestPosts.caption:
📍Dessert Therapy, Malad West (Evershine Nagar, Mumbai)

This isn’t just a dessert store, it’s a pink themed, calming escape in known for its legendary cheesecakes (available in small & regular sizes!) 🎀

✨ Tried & loved:
-> Strawberry & Nutella Cheesecake 
-> Nutella Cheesecake 
-> Triple Chocolate Brownie 
-> My friend went for the Classic Tiramisu — contains alcohol

You can order it via @swiggyindia and @zomato as well 

🌸 Ambience: Cozy, pastel, and perfect for a dessert date or solo treat-yourself day.

🌟 Review:
The desserts are rich in flavor, not overly sweet, and beautifully presented. A must-visit for all dessert enthusiasts in Mumbai! 💕

📌Desert Therapy Mumbai Branches:
* Malad: Evershine Nagar
* Bandra West: Pali Hill
* Juhu: Juhu Tara Road
* Fort: Kala Ghoda
* Ghatkopar: R-city Mall
* Kandivali West: Mathuradas Road
* Andheri East: Chakala
